de.mrms.api
Interface DataRepository

public interface DataRepository

Implementations represent a repository of information about the music catalog, users and their preferences.

getRatedSongIDs

java.util.Set<java.lang.Integer> getRatedSongIDs(java.lang.String username)
Get rated songs of the given user, meaning songs the user has already seen.
Important: This will automatically determine if the user takes part in an Evaluation and then return the appropriate songs. Meaning, if user takes part in an Evaluation it will only return songs seen during the Evaluation.

Parameters:
username - Name of the user
Returns:
Rated song IDs

getRatingsFromUser

java.util.LinkedHashMap<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Double> getRatingsFromUser(java.lang.String username)
Get rated tracks of the given user ordered by rating DESC.
Important: This will automatically determine if the user takes part in an Evaluation and then return the appropriate ratings. Meaning, if user takes part in an Evaluation it will only return ratings done during the Evaluation.

Parameters:
username - The name of the user
Returns:
Mapping of track id -> rating ordered by rating DESC
